{"data":{"_id":"0c2b825f9b","title":"ImageMagick使用","date":"2019-11-04 16:06","update":"2019-11-04 16:06","author":"Rainboy","tags":["linux命令"],"catalog":"学习笔记"},"__content":"<h2 id=\"%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F\" tabindex=\"-1\">大小</h2>\n<p><strong>改变画布的大小,放置到中间位置,设置新增加的区域的颜色为白色</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">convert sample.png -gravity center -background white  -extent 500x500 out.png\n</code></pre>\n"}